Laptops are great for working while travelling or playing games at a LAN, but most people seeking high-end performance revert to desktop PCs. There are certain notebooks on the market which offer both portability and the performance of a high-end PC, however. This is true for professional and gaming applications, as many manufacturers offer high-end workstation laptops ideal for 3D designers and other professionals. These devices can be extremely expensive, but the amount of horsepower delivered is unparalleled. Listed below are the most powerful professional and gaming notebooks available for purchase in South Africa. This powerful MSI workstation boasts an Intel Xeon processor and two NVMe SSDs in a RAID 0 configuration.  The MSI GT75 Titan 8RG packs Intel’s monstrous Core i9 processor and a GeForce GTX 1080.  HP’s mobile workstation packs a powerful Xeon processor paired with a high-speed SSD.  This notebook takes graphics performance to the next level with two Nvidia GeForce GTX 1080 chips.  The high-end notebook features an 8th-gen Core i7 processor and a 144Hz display. 